@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### ============================================
### BASIC PRODUCT QUERIES
### ============================================

### 1. Get All Products (Default Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Products with Custom Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Second Page of Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?page=1&size=5
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### FILTERING BY CATEGORY
### ============================================

### 4. Get Products in Category 1 (Áo Thun)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=1
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get Products in Category 2 (Quần Jean)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=2
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get Products in Category 3 (Giày Dép)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=3
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get Products in Category 4 (Phụ Kiện)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=4
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### FILTERING BY PRICE
### ============================================

### 8. Get Products Under 200k
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?maxPrice=200000
Accept: application/json

### 9. Get Products Between 100k and 500k
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?minPrice=100000&maxPrice=500000
Accept: application/json

### 10. Get Products Over 500k
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?minPrice=500000
Accept: application/json

### 11. Get Affordable Products (50k - 200k)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?minPrice=50000&maxPrice=200000
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### SORTING
### ============================================

### 12. Sort by Price - Low to High
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 13. Sort by Price - High to Low
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=DESC
Accept: application/json

### 14. Sort by Name - A to Z
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=name&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 15. Sort by Name - Z to A
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=name&sortDirection=DESC
Accept: application/json

### 16. Sort by Newest First (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=createdAt&sortDirection=DESC
Accept: application/json

### 17. Sort by Oldest First
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=createdAt&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### COMBINED FILTERS
### ============================================

### 18. Category + Price Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=1&minPrice=100000&maxPrice=300000
Accept: application/json

### 19. Category + Price + Sort
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=2&minPrice=100000&maxPrice=300000&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 20. Full Filter with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=1&minPrice=50000&maxPrice=500000&page=0&size=10&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 21. Expensive Items in Category 3
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=3&minPrice=500000&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=DESC
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### PRODUCT DETAILS
### ============================================

### 22. Get Product by ID - Áo Thun Basic Trắng
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/1
Accept: application/json

### 23. Get Product by ID - Quần Jean Skinny Xanh
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/6
Accept: application/json

### 24. Get Product by Slug - Áo Thun Basic Trắng
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/slug/ao-thun-basic-trang
Accept: application/json

### 25. Get Product by Slug - Giày Sneaker Trắng
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/slug/giay-sneaker-trang
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### EDGE CASES & LARGE QUERIES
### ============================================

### 26. Large Page Size
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?page=0&size=100
Accept: application/json

### 27. Price Range with No Results
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?minPrice=9999999&maxPrice=99999999
Accept: application/json

### 28. High Page Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?page=100&size=10
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### REAL-WORLD SCENARIOS
### ============================================

### 29. Shop Áo T-Shirt Under 300k
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=1&maxPrice=300000&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 30. Browse All Shoes, Cheapest First
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=3&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 31. Find Mid-Range Pants
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=2&minPrice=200000&maxPrice=600000&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

### 32. Browse Premium Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?minPrice=1000000&sortBy=basePrice&sortDirection=DESC
Accept: application/json

### 33. New Arrivals - All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=createdAt&sortDirection=DESC&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### ERROR SCENARIOS
### ============================================

### 34. Product Not Found - Invalid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/99999
Accept: application/json

### 35. Product Not Found - Invalid Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/slug/non-existent-product
Accept: application/json

### 36. Invalid Category ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?categoryId=999
Accept: application/json

### 37. Invalid Sort Field
# > This might be accepted but won't sort properly
GET {{baseUrl}}/product?sortBy=invalidField&sortDirection=ASC
Accept: application/json

